            "body": "> It can be fixed by removing the `_fast` argument.\n\nThat arg only exists for loader :-} https://github.com/neovim/neovim/commit/dcdefd042840c7a6db5dce2963ac23c45a5287da\n\nhowever `path_resolve_dot` was the main cost, so we could try just removing this `_fast` condition: https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/2f8fb4f28ab92d62e07d1d64a6dd89e0b6eb7253/runtime/lua/vim/fs.lua#L629-L630\n\ndoes that fix the issue?\n",
